com.mojang.datafixers.kinds

Interface CartesianLike<T extends K1,C,Mu extends CartesianLike _>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The partially applied product type.
    C - The other type of interest in the product type.
    Mu - The witness type of this functor.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Mu<T>, Functor T, Kind1 T, Traversable T
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Pair.Instance

    public interface CartesianLike<T extends K1,C,Mu extends CartesianLike _>
extends Functor T, Traversable T
    A Traversable functor that operates on a product type, such as a tuple. This type class defines two methods, from(App) and to(App), that convert the type T to and from a Pair.
    See Also:
    Cartesian
